These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, cola, almond-milk
4 different pets are kept: pony, frog, lizard, fish
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk | almond-milk | cola |
| Pet        | pony | frog   | fish | lizard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, spy, horror, zombie
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, egyptian, thai, american
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the italian is on the left of the thai##1
3. the thai is in an odd position##4
4. the italian is the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the egyptian is on the right of the thai##1
6. the italian is the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | time-travel  | spy  | zombie |
| Nationality   | american    | italian | thai | egyptian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, nectarine, asparagus, zucchini
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, drama, time-travel, family
1. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
2. the person eating asparagus is in an even position##4
3. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | zucchini | asparagus | nectarine    | broccoli      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel        | family     | comedy | drama |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, baking, chess, gardening
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, r&b, funk, electronic
1. the person who's hobby is baking is between the fan of salsa and the fan of electronic##2
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the fan of funk is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | gardening | card-games | baking | chess |
| Music-Genre   | funk       | salsa   | r&b    | electronic  |

