.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, indie, metal, r&b
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, indonesian, argentine, pakistani
1. the fan of metal is on the right of the pakistani##1
2. the indonesian is the fan of r&b##1
3. the argentine is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
4. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
5. the fan of metal is in an odd position##4
6. the thai is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | reggae    | metal   | r&b       |
| Nationality   | thai | pakistani | argentine | indonesian |

