3. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
4. the turkish is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the dutch is on the left or right of the turkish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | romance | scientific | adventure |
| Nationality   | mexican | canadian     | turkish  | dutch  |

