.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, superhero, horror, crime
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, trike, train, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person driving the scooter is the person watching documentary movies##1
5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
6. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | crime | horror | superhero    |
| Transport     | scooter | train  | tram     | trike |

