.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, accountant, chef, manager
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, chinchilla, rat, dog
1. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the accountant##3
2. the manager is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the manager##3
4. the manager is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
5. the electrician is between the manager and the accountant##2
6. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the chinchilla is between the electrician and the owner of the rat##2
8. the electrician is on the left or right of the accountant##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | accountant | electrician      | manager | chef |
| Pet   | goldfish  | dog | chinchilla    | rat            |

