.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, pineapple, pomegranate, cauliflower
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goldfish, pony, bird
1. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
2. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the goldfish and the person eating pomegranate##2
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating pomegranate is the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | cauliflower | pineapple   | carrot | pomegranate |
| Pet    | bird     | goldfish | guinea-pig     | pony  |

