.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, tea, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, soul, punk, hip-hop
1. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the fan of metal is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is between the fan of metal and the person drinking tea##2
4. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
6. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | sprite       | tea   | lemonade | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre   | punk | soul | hip-hop        | metal    |

