The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, rugby, golf, parkour
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda   | hot-chocolate   | sprite      | coffee      |
| Sport      | rugby | golf | parkour | weightlifting |

