2. the fan of blues is in an even position##4
3. the person eating grapes is in an even position##4
4. the person eating asparagus is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is between the fan of techno and the fan of blues##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | pineapple | grapes  | cauliflower  | asparagus |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | blues | trance | techno   |

