.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, photography, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, snowboarding, biathlon, handball
1. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | writing | card-games         | camping   | photography |
| Sport   | biathlon    | snowboarding | handball | rugby   |

