.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, dancing, video-games, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, rugby, lacrosse, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
5. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | dancing | photography | video-games    | puzzles |
| Sport   | tennis   | lacrosse  | weightlifting | rugby     |

