.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, fishing, camping, magic-tricks
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, french, pakistani, argentine
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
3. the french is the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the pakistani is on the left or right of the french##3
5. the french is between the argentine and the pakistani##2
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks   | camping | traveling | fishing    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | french  | argentine     | polish |

