.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, tea, lemonade
There 4 different types of food: lemonademelon, artichoke, onion, carrot
1. the person eating artichoke is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
5. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person eating onion is in an even position##4
7. the person eating lemonademelon is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | lemonade | hot-chocolate    | tea       | almond-milk |
| Food       | artichoke  | onion | carrot | lemonademelon  |

