.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, turkish, colombian, nigerian
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, subway, snowmobile, boat
1. the dutch is on the left of the nigerian##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the colombian##1
5. the dutch is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person driving the bike is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | turkish | colombian | dutch  | nigerian |
| Transport     | bike      | snowmobile       | subway | boat     |

