.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, analyst, project-manager, fisherman
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, airplane, quad-bike, roller
1. the analyst is in an even position##4
2. the analyst is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
3. the person driving the airplane is between the social-worker and the person driving the scooter##2
4. the analyst is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the fisherman##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | social-worker | project-manager   | fisherman | analyst |
| Transport   | roller          | airplane | scooter         | quad-bike  |

 